  <brief_title>Does a Single Shot Femoral Nerve Block Alone Produce Appropriate Pain Relief?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Does a Single Shot Femoral Nerve Block Alone Produce Appropriate Pain Relief After Total Knee Arthroplasty or Should an Addition of Sciatic, Obturator and Lateral Femoral Cutaneous Nerve Blocks be Recommended?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Hillel Yaffe Medical Center</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
